description:

・Ignotus / ak+q
・Be There / PSYQUI
・Metallic Punisher / INNOCENT NOIZE
・Modelista / HiTECH NINJA
・Singularity / ETIA.
・Corruption / 3R2
・Grievous Lady / Team Grimoire vs Laur
・Black Lotus / wa.
・GOODTEK / EBIMAYO
・???(Secret)

■Navigator
・HIKARI
・TAIRITSU
・SHIRAHIME

■Avatar
・HIKARI(2D)
・TAIRITSU(2D)
・ETO(2D)
・LUNA(2D)
・SHIRAHIME(2D)

*Some content will be unlocked via missions after downloading.
